### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Meta verify webhook
GET http://localhost:4000/webhooks/whatsapp/meta?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=CHANGE_ME&hub.challenge=12345

### Meta incoming message
POST http://localhost:4000/webhooks/whatsapp/meta
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "entry": [
    {
      "changes": [
        {
          "value": {
            "messages": [
              {
                "id": "wamid.test.001",
                "from": "5215512345678",
                "text": {
                  "body": "Hola, soy persona física y quiero agendar asesoría"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
